{
  "stem": "9113.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we were already seven people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were already seven people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we-- we are trying to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where are we going to go?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then one said, you know what?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We're gonna look for a place which is gonna be a few little trees, not too many trees, and we're gonna make ourselves a bunker.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we're going to stay here, we're going to live here, we're going to see what we have to do.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then, a day-- or two days, I don't remember how long-- came another fellow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This fellow, which I have here a picture of him, and he was a tailor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was older than me already, a few years older.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe 10 years older.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were very happy that we found him, and we are-- and we were trying.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my brother was very capable, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were already eight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When we were already eight people, we were-- we-- we opened, like, a-- we built a bunker.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We went in the-- in the little town-- not a town, a little country place-- and we bought a little stove to make hot water, to boil-- to cook potatoes, a little bit rice, a little bit to live.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "To go on.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then this guy used to take-- he said he's a tailor, and they-- and they-- and they were stealing those blankets from the Russian-- from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we used to make coats for those people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Coats, pants, jackets, everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they gave us bread, they gave us potatoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We didn't have to steal already, we-- we earned it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were there in that place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were there in that place, and this was our life, livelihood.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
